abstract: >
  An MIT-licensed, end-to-end open-source pipeline for hypothesis generation and
  in silico testing of MCAS/MCAD rescue, maintenance, and remission compounds across
  pharma, herbs, and supplements, integrated with AI tooling (PyTDC, DeepChem, REINVENT 4).
